{"url": "people.com/tv/savannah-guthrie-curses-on-today-show/", "text": "Savannah Guthrie is shaking off her Today show hot mic moment.\n\nOn Wednesday, in a rare production mistake of this magnitude for NBC\u2019s flagship morning show, viewers watched Guthrie curse on-air while seemingly preparing for a segment as the shot was accidentally broadcast live.\n\n\u201cOh, s\u2014,\u201d she was heard saying. \u201cSorry, guys.\u201d\n\nGuthrie continued to look down to read and the audio was turned off. After about 30 seconds, the show cut to a Lexus promo.\n\nGuthrie, 46, apologized after the fact on Twitter.\n\n\u201cCheck, check \u2014 is this thing on? Yeah I guess it is. So sorry guys,\u201d she wrote. \u201cThanks for being kind and understanding. And guess it\u2019s [a] good thing I don\u2019t wear a mic all day. #ohdarn.\u201d\n\nOf course, fans were quick to accept her apology and laugh off the incident.\n\n\u201cIt was a funny moment!\u201d wrote one. \u201cWe all need to laugh especially at ourselves.\u201d", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/Lje7sGaj3HgeS-yLg9z5JSNPfrU=/300x150/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/people_magazine_sub-e6689738996d40f38f154099e1751481.png", "https://people.com/thmb/FGESyjSIXAyWLYgGT72ko9BV9VI=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(674x19:676x21)/This-Is-Us-Season-6-db59dee7f0104c8b911d1d8d9226e083.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/weyWWkqxgzhy7mugQ617pHiq9RI=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(999x0:1001x2)/beyonce-jay-z-7cbd2fe52a774f10a51fb215443cc159.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/DZhU-zoyW73aRpVcEQCY_ZwgEGA=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(689x297:691x299)/the-view-e65f304fac4b4a028c84e655a3fc03bb.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/142TpjTaD8Bh59u5L6DoZUAMSzk=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(459x149:461x151)/kim-burrell-red-carpet-072122-9e07d7c90acd49dc8f739121a5e7572d.jpg", "https://people